text: Very very yummy and delicious Hainanese baoluo noodle! Even a very authentic recipe for their beef is handmade, making the noodle more tasty . Definitely will order again !  Have dry and soup options, I have order both, I prefer the soup one is much more savory!
very yummy! satisfied my late night craving! beef was soft, tender and full of flavor!
SUPER Yummy Hainan beef noodle ~! Definitely will buy again , I can eat 2 bowls at one time hahaha!
Super yummy!!!!! Tried the beef gravy one!! Will definitely try other ones in future. Strongly recommend everyone to have a try!
